in a more comfortable chair than me,

127
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:05,033
I can make them sit in that chair,

128
00:11:05,033 --> 00:11:06,933
whoever they are.

129
00:11:10,767 --> 00:11:13,133
What is it that

130
