Yes, I do.

134
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:33,733
Success is...

135
00:11:33,733 --> 00:11:35,267
No,

136
00:11:35,267 --> 00:11:37,600
being rich,

137
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:42,200
