142
00:12:07,967 --> 00:12:12,933
There's something I want to do in here,

143
00:12:12,933 --> 00:12:16,167
but I can't anymore.

144
00:12:16,167 --> 00:12:17,800
I want you, Kang Yeo Reum,

145
00:12:18,533 --> 00:12:21,767
