146
00:12:23,033 --> 00:12:26,300
To help you get what you want,

147
00:12:26,300 --> 00:12:28,833
I'll pay you generously for it.

148
00:12:28,833 --> 00:12:31,300
If you take what I tell you to do

149
00:12:31,300 --> 00:12:35,800
