160
00:13:42,367 --> 00:13:45,333
<i>If I complete these trips you mentioned,</i>

161
00:13:45,333 --> 00:13:47,367
<i>please revive</i>

162
00:13:47,367 --> 00:13:49,633
<i>the Day Trip program.</i>

163
00:13:50,400 --> 00:13:54,400
