170
00:14:09,933 --> 00:14:12,767
Ah, of course, you absolutely should.

171
00:14:12,767 --> 00:14:15,367
Alright, let's go up, have dinner, and head home.

172
00:14:15,367 --> 00:14:17,433
Oh, once I get there,

173
00:14:17,433 --> 00:14:19,433
