Yes.

206
00:17:14,267 --> 00:17:16,033
It'll work out.

207
00:17:19,733 --> 00:17:22,900
It's a fresh start, Kang Yeo Reum.

208
00:17:29,233 --> 00:17:30,967
You rejected it?

209
00:17:32,300 --> 00:17:34,800
That's how it went.

210
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:36,833
