212
00:17:39,033 --> 00:17:42,067
What kind of conditions don't match
that you'd throw away such an opportunity?

213
00:17:42,067 --> 00:17:45,933
It's not just about missing the chance.

214
00:17:45,933 --> 00:17:47,133
