219
00:17:57,867 --> 00:17:58,900
No.

220
00:17:58,900 --> 00:18:01,333
Eat well, Mr. O.

221
00:18:01,333 --> 00:18:03,800
Isn't this situation funny?

222
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:05,633
Oh, what was that?

223
00:18:05,633 --> 00:18:07,100
Scratching the back of your head.

224
