235
00:18:36,967 --> 00:18:39,133
Look at the sweat on your nose.

236
00:18:39,133 --> 00:18:42,533
Your 'truth spring' activates when lying, right?

237
00:18:42,533 --> 00:18:43,900
Here.

238
00:18:43,900 --> 00:18:45,833
